ing: 2 (6 ounce) cans crabmeat, drained and flaked
des: "This dip is gets demolished every time I make it. Simple ingredients give unbelievable flavor when mixed together -- cream cheese, crab, shrimp, onion, tomato, garlic, and banana peppers served with tortillas chips. You won't regret serving this!"
ins: Melt the cream cheese in a fondue pot. Gently fold in tomato, onion, garlic, crab, shrimp, and peppers.
